# Operating systems - KX Delta Platform

Original URL: https://code.kx.com/platform/deployment/prerequisites/

# Supported operating systems

The _KX Delta Platform_ is supported on the following Operating Systems:

## Linux

### Kdb Insights

If kdb Insights is underpinning KX Delta Platform, which is the default from
version 4.8.0, not all of the above distributions will be supported, the
requirements of kdb Insights must be met

  * requires openssl1.1-compatible libraries and libcurl at least version 7.31
  * libc.so.6 version GLIBC_2.14 required, therefore RHEL6 and CentoOS 6 not supported
  * kdb Insights documentation  [kdb Insights](https://code.kx.com/insights/1.3/core/prereqs.html)

## Windows

